org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.process.traversal.step

Interface LambdaHolder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LambdaCollectingBarrierStep, LambdaFilterStep, LambdaFlatMapStep, LambdaMapStep, LambdaSideEffectStep, SackValueStep

    public interface LambdaHolder
    This is a marker interface stating that the Step contains a lambda/anonymous function. This information is typically used by a TraversalStrategy in a verification stage as lambdas are not serializable and thus, can not be propagated over the network.
    Author:
    Marko A. Rodriguez (http://markorodriguez.com)
